<HEAD>2 THE NUN'S PRIEST'S END-LINK. [Incipit prologus fabule secunde monialis</HEAD><HEADNOTE>[<I>Addit. MS</I> 5140, <I>Brit. Mus., leaf</I> 282, <I>back</I> (<I>paper</I>).]</HEADNOTE>

