<DIV1 TYPE="link"><PB REF="00000712.tif" N="28*"><MILESTONE UNIT="6-text p" N="167">
<HEAD>3. THE MAN-OF-LAW&mdash;SHIPMAN LINK. The prolog of the squyers tale</HEAD><HEADNOTE><P><I>Royal MS</I> 18 <I>C ii, leaf</I> 82 (<I>Brit. Mus.</I>).</P></HEADNOTE>
<LG TYPE="stanza">
<L>OWre oost vp on his stiropes stood a-non</L>
<L>And saide godemen herkeneth euerichon</L>
<L>This was a thrifty tale for &thorn;e nones</L>
<L N="1166">Sire parisshe preest quod he for goddes bones</L>
